A Magistrates’ Court in Makurdi, on Monday, ordered that a farmer, Saater Oraduen, charged with illegal possession of a firearm, be remanded in a correctional facility, pending legal advice, Magistrate Ajuma Igama did not take the plea of Oraduen because her court lacked the jurisdiction to hear the case. Igama ordered that Oraduen be remanded at the Federal Correctional Centre Makurdi and adjourned the case until Feb 24 for further mention. Earlier, the Prosecution Counsel, Sgt. Ato Godwin, told the court that Oraduen was arrested by the Joint task force, led by LT. A. I Gidado in Katsina-Ala, Benue. ALSO READ: Ekiti gets first female Head of Service NGOs lament poor budget line for adolescent health services Court slams 10 years jail term on rapist in Kogi BREAKING: Obaseki petitions IGP over Edo APC crisis Brain drain, hindrance to health sector development ― Expert Ato said, the troop, while on routine patrol in Katsina-Ala town, received information that Oraduen, was seen with a gun attempting to rob a woman on the Katsina-Ala head bridge. The team, he said, arrested Oraduen, who resides in Katsina-Ala L.G.A, Benue, with a locally made pistol. During the police investigation, he said, the suspect allegedly confessed to the crime and gave out the name of his accomplice, one Terpase, currently at large. The offence, he said, contravened the provisions of sections 6(b) and 3(1) of the Robbery and Firearms Special Provisions Act, 2004. (NAN) SHOCKING LIFE STORY!!! Abuja Man reveals (FREE) secret Fruits that Increased his Manh0d size and Lasting Power in just 7days… CLICK HERE TO GET IT!!! STAY STRONGER, LONGER AND SATISFY MADAM LIKE NEVER BEFORE WITH THIS NATURAL SUPPLEMENTS WITH NO SIDE EFFECTS. CLICK NOW. CLICK HERE NOW TO WORK FROM HOME ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN CONVINIENCE AND GET PAID WEEKLY, DIRECTLY INTO YOUR SPECIFIED BANK ACCOUNT.REGISTRATION IS ABSOLUTELY FREE. PREMATURE EJACULATION, SMALL SIZE FINALLY CURED NATURALLY IN 2 WEEKS FOR BIGGER, LONGER, HARDER SEXI